19
00:00:59,540 --> 00:01:01,190
Do you want to date me?

20
00:01:04,769 --> 00:01:06,410
So…

21
00:01:06,410 --> 00:01:09,150
Seol Dongbaek, let's date.

22
00:01:09,150 --> 00:01:11,400
